questions.quote: So, it's Monica and Chandler. I only know you as file 0W33815-D.
Well hey, I wanna ask you about Monica's little "groomy" joke.
Okay. Then I guess it's just, wait here then. Hi. I need one fake ticket to Yemen.
Ok, how about this: We got wind up toys for Emma for her birthday. We can make them race, and whoever comes in last, stays!
Shh. Shh. Don't try to talk, we'll get you up to your room, we'll soak your feet, you'll be okay.
Oh no. Could I get anyone a coffee or...poison? No? Just for me? Okay.
Well I'm jumping! I have a son! Okay? He won't have a father if-if I die!
No-no-no, please-please Chandler I-I-I would owe you so much!
'Okay. Okay, daddy we'll see you tomorrow night. Okay bye-bye.'
What?! I thought he'd love it! His favorite kid's book was the Velveteen Rabbit!
